{
  "stem": "21550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My future wife then was living a couple of buildings away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would like to come to see her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to break through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to go to the-- to the attics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, go through from one to the other, until we reached her-- her building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But like I said, they didn't help any.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't do anything-- anything whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- I said that everybody tries to rescue themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They try to get away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were a lot of people, a lot of Jews, who had relations with Poles-- whether business, professional.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they tried to solicit them to-- to do something, to help, at least to help their friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them helped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my wife and I survived by being hidden from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This happened-- my wife's sister had connections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And she was given names and addresses of people who might help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So through them, she was able to buy an apartment, or rent an apartment, which was part of the ghetto, until they made it smaller, until they-- Every time they took 10-- or 20,000 people out of the ghetto, they closed a street and incorporated that in the rest of the-- of the-- of the-- of city.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they rented an apartment, which was formerly-- formerly, a few weeks before, part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But not anymore.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she brought 19 people into this apartment to hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Unfortunately, after about four-- four to five weeks, somebody uncovered, and the next thing was they sent a blackmail with a German soldier to this apartment and knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
